<br>
Basic Requirements :<br>
1) You are an active EQ player and willing to raid a lot.<br>
<br>
2) Your main character must be a lv 60 character.<br>
<br>
3) You are expected to raid with us a lot before you got your membership.<br>
Raiding period depends on how much we know you, how active you are, ..etc.<br>
<br>
4) You need to follow guild direction tightly.<br>
<br>
5) Must have good attitube towards raids and not to be rude to other guildmembers.<br>
<br>
6) You are supposed to know how your class works in both raid and exp group situation.<br>
<br>
7) Full set resist gears.<br>
<br>
8. You must know your way to the raiding zones well and dun expect help on port etc.<br>
<br>
9) You must be able to move your char fast enough once raid call is made.<br>
<br>
10) All expansion enabled.<br>
<br>
<br>
The following information MUST be provided :<br>
1) Guild history/background.<br>
<br>
2) Real owner from the beginning or its a E-char, must be clarified.<br>
<br>
3) Your active timezone specify in PST/HKT time slots.<br>
<br>
4) How many AA pts.<br>
<br>
<br>
<br>
Hints (Not a must):<br>
1) A brief introduction of yourself in the world of EQ, how long you played in EQ, why you want to join zs.<br>
<br>
2) Tell us your reference persons in ZS, or any friends you know in ZS.<br>
<br>
3) List of key rings.<br>
<br>
4) A link of megalo profile.<br>
<br>
5) Listing of the AA skills would be better. <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagefrm8.showPrevMessage?topicID=240.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagefrm8.showNextMessage?topicID=240.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br></td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagefrm8.emailToFriend?topicID=240.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagefrm8.threadControl?topicID=240.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/classic/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagefrm8.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=240.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub17.ezboard.com/fzenithsagefrm8.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=240.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub17.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="zenithsagepublic">Public<option value="zenithsagemembersonly">Members Only<option value="zenithsagegmofficersonly">GM & Officers Only<option value="zenithsagefrm4">Treasure<option value="zenithsagefrm5">Member List<option value="zenithsagefrm6">ZS Market<option value="zenithsagefrm7">Quest items area<option value="zenithsagefrm8">Recruit<option value="zenithsagefrm9">la Pucelle</select></td><td><input type=submit value="Go" class=inputbutton></td></tr></table><